殡仪馆车辆运送生活物资，武汉黄陂通报：殡葬所所长被免职。
Funerary vehicles to transport living materials, Wuhan Huangpi notice: the funeral director was dismissed.
黄陂区政府网站​。
Web site of Huangpi District Government.
