界面新闻。
Interface news.
界面新闻是中国具有影响力的原创财经新媒体，只服务于独立思考的人群。
Interface News is an original and influential new financial media in China, serving only the people who think independently.
图片来源：图虫来源：黄陂区政府网站作者：黄陂区政府网站“ 3月14日晚8时50分，黄陂区委、区纪委发现江岸区海赋社区微信群反映“社区用殡仪馆车辆运送团购物资”，立即组织核实处理。
At 8: 50 pm on March 14, the Huangpi District District Committee and District Disciplinary Committee of Huangpi District have discovered that the micro-trust group of Haifu community in Jiangan District reflects the "Community Funeral Service Vehicle to transport the group's purchases" and immediately organize the verification and handling.
”3月14日晚8时50分，黄陂区委、区纪委发现江岸区海赋社区微信群反映“社区用殡仪馆车辆运送团购物资”，立即组织核实处理。
At 8: 50 p.m. on March 14, District Disciplinary Committee of Huangpi District District Committee discovered that the micro-trust group of Haifu community in Jiangan District reflected the "Community Funeral Service Vehicle to transport the group purchase material" and immediately organized the verification and handling.
经查，当日下午3时20分左右，黄陂区乡镇殡葬车辆社会承包人吕某违规用所承包经营的殡葬用车给家住江岸区海赋江城小区的亲戚陈某运送生活物资，所送生活物资系殡葬用车承包人吕某个人购买，不是社区团购物资。
It is found that at about 3.20 p.m. on the same day, Lu Mou, a social contractor of township funeral vehicles of Huangpi District, illegally used contracted funeral vehicles to deliver living materials to Chen Mou, a relative of the district of Haifu Jiangcheng District.
吕某的行为造成不良社会影响。
Lu's behavior has caused adverse social effects.
经黄陂区纪委研究并报区委同意，对区殡葬管理所所长敖浩予以免职，并党纪立案审查；对区民政局党组成员、副局长骆文俊予以党纪立案审查；责成区殡葬管理所解除与吕某殡葬用车承包经营协议，并依法追究违约责任。
Investigating and reporting to the District Committee, the chairman of the District Funeral Management Office of Huangpi District has been dismissed and the party disciplinary case examined.
。
